<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Television_coverage">Television coverage</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=1988_Major_League_Baseball_season&amp;action=edit&amp;section=16" title="Edit section: Television coverage"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<table class="wikitable">
<tbody><tr>
<th>Network</th>
<th>Day of week</th>
<th>Announcers
