</td>
<td><a href="/wiki/Monday_Night_Baseball" title="Monday Night Baseball">Monday nights</a>
</td>
<td><a href="/wiki/Al_Michaels" title="Al Michaels">Al Michaels</a>, <a href="/wiki/Jim_Palmer" title="Jim Palmer">Jim Palmer</a>, <a href="/wiki/Tim_McCarver" title="Tim McCarver">Tim McCarver</a>, <a href="/wiki/Gary_Bender" title="Gary Bender">Gary Bender</a>, <a href="/wiki/Joe_Morgan" title="Joe Morgan">Joe Morgan</a>, <a href="/wiki/Reggie_Jackson" title="Reggie Jackson">Reggie Jackson</a>
