<li id="cite_note-br_tor-7"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-br_tor_7-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite class="citation web cs1"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.baseball-reference.com/teams/TOR/attend.shtml">"Toronto Blue Jays Attendance, Stadiums and Park Factors"</a>. <a href="/wiki/Baseball-Reference.com" title="Baseball-Reference.com">Baseball-Reference.com</a><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">September 8,</span> 2020</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Toronto+Blue+Jays+Attendance%2C+Stadiums+and+Park+Factors&amp;rft.pub=Baseball-Reference.com&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.baseball-reference.com%2Fteams%2FTOR%2Fattend.shtml&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3A1988+Major+League+Baseball+season" class="Z3988"></span></span>
</li>
